{"tid":2186781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"只有男明星才有「紳士腿」？都來看看IZ*ONE張員瑛的「淑女腿」XD","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T08:38:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dffae31c973012c6ce86ae1e7d0681ebc4cb44b4","tid":2186781,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:56:20.000Z","msg":"所謂紳士腿，就是男明星們把一雙大長腿劈開，壓低身高，照顧身邊人。 但「紳士腿」並不僅僅局限在男星身上，身材高挑的IZ*ONE成員張員瑛也有，稱為「淑女腿」是不是更貼切?<br />\n<br />\n日前曝光的IZ*ONE YouTube影片中，張員瑛被發現使用了「淑女腿」。 男性工作人員正在為張員瑛整理頭髮，看到對方身高不是特別高，張員瑛很乖巧地劈開大長腿，將身高拉低到工作人員不費勁就能碰觸的高度，貼心一面讓人好感度大增。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_fcb0e004f04f3444b2123da02ede1884/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-02/129741-870588.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_fcb0e004f04f3444b2123da02ede1884%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-02%2F129741-870588.jpeg&h=3d8e3798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年17歲的張員瑛雖然尚未成年，但身高已經有171cm了，那雙筆直的鉛筆大長腿最是讓人羨慕了。張員瑛也意識到自己在女愛豆中算是高個子，會有意識地照顧身邊人，參加《Produce 48》的時候，站上獎台的她也劈開了腿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_3a03fb98fef71d51ec96df691be11672/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-09-02/129741-870592.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_3a03fb98fef71d51ec96df691be11672%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-09-02%2F129741-870592.png&h=92890d54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fdb25366a6aa97cdcf306ff8011a666b01f80ee","tid":2186781,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d4e8ea9ea3bda0383b7a43f3aa04c69ab507a8","tid":2186781,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0fdb25366a6aa97cdcf306ff8011a666b01f80ee","tid":2186781,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:57:53.000Z","msg":"好乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumb.pann.com/tc_480/https://fimg4.pann.com/new/download.jsp?FileID=48544237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumb.pann.com%2Ftc_480%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Ffimg4.pann.com%2Fnew%2Fdownload.jsp%3FFileID%3D48544237&h=05563899&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ec47f99e5d8c97ced550cb990eea07663b166cd","tid":2186781,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"我妹!!❤"},{"pid":"a646742c43654f5cebbd747d9b597052a25c7005","tid":2186781,"uid":313222,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"17碎就挽到合吾埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9b7c44a3fee838a583c7ac79e6a2551c61b155","tid":2186781,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"乖女☺️"},{"pid":"01d43a57aa88cda18bdd50d05c2881478ac02aa8","tid":2186781,"uid":203993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"老江湖.jpg"}]}